</title>
<link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="https://mjtsai.com/blog/2019/11/04/electron-apps-rejected-from-the-mac-app-store/"/>
<link rel="shorturl" type="text/html" href="http://df4.us/ry9"/>
<link rel="related" type="text/html" href="https://daringfireball.net/linked/2019/11/05/electron-mac-app-store"/>
