<title>
Read the Letter Facebook Employees Sent to Mark Zuckerberg About Political Ads
</title>
<link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="https://www.nytimes.com/2019/10/28/technology/facebook-mark-zuckerberg-letter.html"/>
