<title>
Facebook Allows Prominent Right-Wing Website to Break the Rules
</title>
<link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="https://popular.info/p/facebook-allows-prominent-right-wing"/>
<link rel="shorturl" type="text/html" href="http://df4.us/rxl"/>
<link rel="related" type="text/html" href="https://daringfireball.net/linked/2019/10/28/facebook-daily-wire-legum"/>
